<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MAINDUSA | Mantenimiento Industrial Arevalo</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        /* =========================================
           VARIABLES CSS & CONFIGURACIÓN BASE
        ========================================= */
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #050507;
            --bg-card: #0d0d11;
            --bg-card-hover: #15151c;
            --text-main: #f0f0f5;
            --text-muted: #8b8b99;
            --accent-primary: #ff6b00; /* Naranja Fuego */
            --accent-secondary: #ffb300; /* Amarillo Chispa */
            --metal-light: #e0e4e8;
            --metal-dark: #4a4e59;
            --border-color: #22252e;
            --font-main: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            --transition-smooth: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* =========================================
           UTILIDADES Y COMPONENTES
        ========================================= */
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .section-padding {
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 60px;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--metal-light), var(--metal-dark));
            border-radius: 0px;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 50px auto;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            border-radius: 0px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            border: none;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--accent-primary);
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.3);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .btn-primary::before {
            display: none;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translate(-3px, -3px);
            box-shadow: 7px 7px 0px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.6);
            background: var(--accent-secondary);
            border-color: var(--accent-secondary);
            color: #000;
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            color: var(--metal-light);
            border: 2px solid var(--metal-dark);
            box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px rgba(74, 78, 89, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: var(--metal-dark);
            color: #fff;
            transform: translate(-3px, -3px);
            box-shadow: 7px 7px 0px rgba(74, 78, 89, 0.6);
        }

        /* =========================================
           NAVBAR (HEADER)
        ========================================= */
        .navbar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background: rgba(7, 7, 9, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .navbar .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #000, -1px -1px 0 #000, 1px -1px 0 #000, -1px 1px 0 #000, 1px 1px 0 #000;
        }

        .logo span {
            color: #fff;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            position: relative;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .nav-links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0%;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--accent-primary);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .menu-toggle {
            display: none;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* =========================================
           HERO SECTION
        ========================================= */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding-top: 80px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-bg {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: 
                linear-gradient(to right, rgba(7, 7, 9, 0.95) 20%, rgba(7, 7, 9, 0.6) 100%),
                url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504917595217-d4dc5ebe6122?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
            z-index: -2;
            animation: kenburns 20s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .hero-particles {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; right: 0; width: 50%; height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%);
            z-index: -1;
            animation: pulseGlow 4s infinite alternate;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1) forwards;
        }

        .hero-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.1);
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            padding: 6px 15px;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-primary);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .hero-title span {
            color: transparent;
            -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--metal-dark);
            position: relative;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff 0%, #888c96 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .hero-title span::before {
            content: "INDUSTRIAL";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            color: var(--metal-light);
            width: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: fillText 3s ease-in-out forwards 1s;
            border-right: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);
            -webkit-text-stroke: 0px;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        /* =========================================
           BENEFITS SECTION
        ========================================= */
        .benefits {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            position: relative;
        }

        .benefits-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .benefit-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--bg-card), #0a0a0d);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-top: 4px solid var(--metal-dark);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 0px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .benefit-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -4px; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-primary), var(--accent-secondary));
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transform-origin: left;
            transition: transform 0.4s ease;
        }

        .benefit-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            background: var(--bg-card-hover);
            border-color: rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.2);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
        }

        .benefit-card:hover::before {
            transform: scaleX(1);
        }

        .icon-box {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
            background: rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.2);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .benefit-card:hover .icon-box {
            background: var(--accent-primary);
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
        }

        /* SVG Icons Customizados */
        .icon-box svg {
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
            fill: var(--accent-primary);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .benefit-card:hover .icon-box svg {
            fill: #fff;
        }

        .benefit-title {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .benefit-text {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* =========================================
           SERVICES SECTION
        ========================================= */
        .services {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-dark) 0%, #0d0d12 100%);
        }

        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .service-card {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 0px;
            overflow: hidden;
            group: hover;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .service-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.6s ease;
            filter: grayscale(80%) brightness(0.6);
        }

        .service-card:hover .service-img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            filter: grayscale(0%) brightness(0.8);
        }

        .service-content {
            padding: 30px;
            position: relative;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-top: 3px solid var(--metal-dark);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .service-card:hover .service-content {
            border-top-color: var(--accent-primary);
            background: var(--bg-card-hover);
        }

        .service-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .service-desc {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .service-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .service-link::after {
            content: '→';
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .service-link:hover::after {
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        /* =========================================
           WOW SECTION (HIGHLIGHT)
        ========================================= */
        .highlight-section {
            position: relative;
            padding: 120px 0;
            background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533090161767-e6ffed986c88?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80') fixed center/cover;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .highlight-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(7, 7, 9, 0.85);
        }

        .highlight-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .highlight-title {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .highlight-text {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* =========================================
           PROCESS SECTION
        ========================================= */
        .process {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
        }

        .process-steps {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .process-steps::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 40px;
            left: 10%;
            right: 10%;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--border-color);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .process-steps::before { display: none; }
        }

        .step-item {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 220px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .step-number {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--metal-dark), var(--bg-dark));
            border: 2px solid var(--metal-light);
            clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 100% 50%, 50% 100%, 0% 50%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--metal-light);
            margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .step-item:hover .step-number {
            background: var(--accent-primary);
            border-color: var(--accent-secondary);
            color: #000;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .step-title {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .step-text {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* =========================================
           GALLERY / PORTFOLIO
        ========================================= */
        .portfolio {
            background: var(--bg-card);
        }

        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
            aspect-ratio: 4/3;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .gallery-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .gallery-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.85);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }

        .gallery-item:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .gallery-item:hover .gallery-overlay {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .gallery-icon {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* =========================================
           CTA FINAL SECTION
        ========================================= */
        .cta-final {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111, #000);
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--accent-primary);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-primary);
            position: relative;
        }

        .cta-final::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(255,107,0,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .cta-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* =========================================
           FOOTER
        ========================================= */
        .footer {
            background-color: #040405;
            padding: 60px 0 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .footer-col h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .footer-col p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .footer-logo {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .footer-logo span {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .contact-info strong {
            color: #fff;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .social-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .social-icon:hover {
            background: var(--accent-primary);
            border-color: var(--accent-primary);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        /* =========================================
           ANIMACIONES (KEYFRAMES)
        ========================================= */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes kenburns {
            from { transform: scale(1); }
            to { transform: scale(1.05); }
        }

        @keyframes pulseGlow {
            from { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.9); }
            to { opacity: 0.8; transform: scale(1.1); }
        }

        @keyframes fillText {
            from { width: 0; }
            to { width: 100%; }
        }

        /* =========================================
           RESPONSIVE DESIGN (MEDIA QUERIES)
        ========================================= */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .hero-title { font-size: 3.5rem; }
            .section-title { font-size: 2.2rem; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-links {
                display: none; /* En producción requiere JS para menu hamburguesa */
            }
            .menu-toggle {
                display: block;
            }
            .hero-title { font-size: 2.8rem; }
            .hero-buttons { flex-direction: column; }
            .hero-content { text-align: center; }
            .hero-tag { margin: 0 auto 20px auto; }
            .section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
            .highlight-title { font-size: 2.2rem; }
            .cta-title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .process-steps { flex-direction: column; gap: 30px; }
            .step-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- NAVBAR -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <a href="#" class="logo">MAIN<span>DUSA</span></a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#inicio">Inicio</a></li>
                <li><a href="#beneficios">Beneficios</a></li>
                <li><a href="#servicios">Servicios</a></li>
                <li><a href="#portafolio">Proyectos</a></li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 0.85rem;">Contactar</a>
            <div class="menu-toggle">☰</div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <header id="inicio" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-bg"></div>
        <div class="hero-particles"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <span class="hero-tag">Mantenimiento Industrial Arevalo</span>
                <h1 class="hero-title">Soluciones de <span>INDUSTRIAL</span><br>Al Más Alto Nivel</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">Optimizamos el rendimiento de su maquinaria, infraestructura y estructuras metálicas con estándares de calidad, soldadura especializada y seguridad incomparables.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary">Cotizar Proyecto</a>
                    <a href="#servicios" class="btn btn-outline">Nuestros Servicios</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- BENEFICIOS SECTION -->
    <section id="beneficios" class="benefits section-padding">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">¿Por Qué Elegirnos?</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Garantizamos precisión técnica, robustez y durabilidad en cada proyecto industrial que ejecutamos.</p>
            
            <div class="benefits-grid">
                <!-- Tarjeta 1 -->
                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="icon-box">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="benefit-title">Estructuras Sólidas</h3>
                    <p class="benefit-text">Fabricación y mantenimiento de estructuras diseñadas para soportar las condiciones más exigentes.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Tarjeta 2 -->
